  "runtime": "python",
  "linuxFxVersion": "Python|3.12",
  "environment": {
    "MY_VAR": "hello"
  }
}
</code></pre></p> <p><code>linuxFxVersion</code> is optional. When set, floci-az selects the matching Azure Functions Linux image, such as <code>mcr.microsoft.com/azure-functions/python:4-python3.12</code>. The ARM-compatible <code>Microsoft.Web/sites</code> and <code>Microsoft.Web/sites/{name}/config/web</code> paths accept the same setting under <code>properties.siteConfig.linuxFxVersion</code> and <code>properties.linuxFxVersion</code>, respectively.</p>

